dataQuality.description: High-quality regulatory data with minimal revisions

api_documentation.description: Socrata API documentation (platform powering CFTC data)

setup: No authentication required - start querying immediately
Choose appropriate dataset from 12 working endpoints
Use limit parameter to control response size
Apply date filters for specific time periods
workflow: 1. Identify the report type needed (Legacy, Disaggregated, TFF, or CIT)
2. Select futures-only, combined, or aggregated version
4. Set date range and limit parameters
5. Parse response JSON for positioning data
gotchas: Data released weekly on Fridays for Tuesday close
Some datasets start from 2006, others from 1986
Field names vary slightly between datasets
Large result sets may need pagination
Commercial positions include index traders in some reports
